gn System: played a key role in developing and refining VK's design system (VKUI)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-1\",{\"children\":\"Optimized image filters to speed up main feed load times by switching from Accelerate to CoreImage and streamlining the render pipeline to a single pass\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-2\",{\"children\":\"Skills: Swift, Obj-C, UIKit, SwiftUI, TextKit, CoreGraphics, CoreAnimation, CoreImage, Metal, Accelerate, XCTest, MetricKit.\"}]]}],null]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Lecturer at ITMO University\",{\"className\":\"Profile_experience__8pQJc\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_year__KzJ4a\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"2023 — 2024\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_title__DhufJ\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://en.itmo.ru/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"children\":\"Lecturer at ITMO University\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_linkArrow__Kwzq5\",\"children\":[\"﻿\",[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"width\":\"12\",\"height\":\"12\",\"viewBox\":\"0 0 12 12\",\"fill\":\"none\",\"xmlns\":\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M3.5 3C3.22386 3 3 3.22386 3 3.5C3 3.77614 3.22386 4 3.5 4V3ZM8.5 3.5H9C9 3.22386 8.77614 3 8.5 3V3.5ZM8 8.5C8 8.77614 8.22386 9 8.5 9C8.77614 9 9 8.77614 9 8.5H8ZM2.64645 8.64645C2.45118 8.84171 2.45118 9.15829 2.64645 9.35355C2.84171 9.54882 3.15829 9.54882 3.35355 9.35355L2.64645 8.64645ZM3.5 4H8.5V3H3.5V4ZM8 3.5V8.5H9V3.5H8ZM8.14645 3.14645L2.64645 8.64645L3.35355 9.35355L8.85355 3.85355L8.14645 3.14645Z\",\"fill\":\"var(--grey1)\"}]}]]}]]}],null,[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_description__OMT9q\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-0\",{\"children\":\"Delivered lectures on iOS development, conducted live coding sessions, and evaluated student assignments\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-1\",{\"children\":[\"Publications: \",[\"$\",\"a\",\"a-0\",{\"href\":\"https://education.vk.company/program/237\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"children\":\"Course announcement\"}]]}]]}],null]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"iOS Engineer at SuperApp Team at VK\",{\"className\":\"Profile_experience__8pQJc\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_year__KzJ4a\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"2023 — 2024\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_title__DhufJ\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"http://vk.com\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"children\":\"iOS Engineer at SuperApp Team at VK\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_linkArrow__Kwzq5\",\"children\":[\"﻿\",[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"width\":\"12\",\"height\":\"12\",\"viewBox\":\"0 0 12 12\",\"fill\":\"none\",\"xmlns\":\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M3.5 3C3.22386 3 3 3.22386 3 3.5C3 3.77614 3.22386 4 3.5 4V3ZM8.5 3.5H9C9 3.22386 8.77614 3 8.5 3V3.5ZM8 8.5C8 8.77614 8.22386 9 8.5 9C8.77614 9 9 8.77614 9 8.5H8ZM2.64645 8.64645C2.45118 8.84171 2.45118 9.15829 2.64645 9.35355C2.84171 9.54882 3.15829 9.54882 3.35355 9.35355L2.64645 8.64645ZM3.5 4H8.5V3H3.5V4ZM8 3.5V8.5H9V3.5H8ZM8.14645 3.14645L2.64645 8.64645L3.35355 9.35355L8.85355 3.85355L8.14645 3.14645Z\",\"fill\":\"var(--grey1)\"}]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_location__j4kBh\",\"children\":\"Saint Petersburg, Russia\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_description__OMT9q\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-0\",{\"children\":\"Service's showcase: rebuilt main navigation entry point for VK App users from the ground up, creating a complex interactive collection with multiple sections, custom layout logic, realtime SSE updates, custom collection view animations\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-1\",{\"children\":\"Service's showcase settings: implemented widgets settings, so users can customize the showcase to their needs. Implemented custom drag-n-drop logic similar to springboard mechanic\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-2\",{\"children\":\"TabBar customization: this feature allows users to setup their tabbar by selecting most used tabs. Led the development of the whole feature with the most 'fun' part of disassembling UIKit to find private API's to allow more than 5 tabs on iOS devices\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-3\",{\"children\":[\"Publications: \",[\"$\",\"a\",\"a-0\",{\"href\":\"https://m.vk.com/wall-35005_54964\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"children\":\"Tab Bar settings release\"}]]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",\"p-4\",{\"children\":\"Skills: Swift, Obj-C, UIKit, CoreGraphics, CoreAnimation, Lottie, RLottie, Swift Structured Concurrency, GCD, HealthKit, Combine, Yoga.\"}]]}],null]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Junior iOS Engineer at SuperApp Team at VK\",{\"className\":\"Profile_experience__8pQJc\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_year__KzJ4a\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"2022 — 2023\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"$undefined\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_title__DhufJ\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"http://vk.com\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"children\":\"Junior iOS Engineer at SuperApp Team at VK\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"Profile_linkArrow__Kwzq5\",\"children\":[\"﻿\",[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"width\":\"12\",\"height\":\"12\",\"viewBox\":\"0 0 12 12\",\"fill\":\"none\",\"xmlns\":\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M3.5 3C3.22386 3 3 3.22386 3 3.5C3 3.77614 3.22386 4 3.5 4V3ZM8.5 3.5H9C9 3.22386 8.77614 3 8.5 3V3.5ZM8 8.5C8 8.77614 8.22386 9 8.5 9C8.77614 9 9 8.77614 9 8.5H8ZM2.64645 8.64645C2.45118 8.84171 2.45118 9.15829 2.64645 9.35355C2.84171 9.54882 3.15829 9.54882 3.35355 9.35355L2.64645 8.64645ZM3.5 4H8.5V3H3.5V4ZM8 3.5V8.5H9V3.5H8ZM8.14645 3.14645L2.64645 8.64645L3.35355 9.35355L8.85355 3.85355L8.14645 3.14645Z\",\"fill\":\"var(--grey1)\"}]}]]}]]}],null,[\"$\",\"di